"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                    <use href=\"#dot\"><\/use>\n                <\/svg>\n              Let\u2019s build you something that finally does your agency justice.            <\/div>\n                                <h2 class=\"text-35\"><p>Your own website always comes last&#8230; we get it<\/p>\n<\/h2>\n          \n                      <div\n              class=\"content sm:w-11\/12 lg:w-full\">\n              <p>If you\u2019re a digital, creative, or marketing agency, you know how it goes:<\/p>\n<p>\u2022 Clients come first.<br \/>\n\u2022 Campaigns take priority.<br \/>\n\u2022 Your own web build? Always \u201cnext quarter.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>We\u2019ve been there. As an agency ourselves, we understand how easy it is to let your own site (and marketing) fall to the bottom of the backlog. But your website is more than a portfolio &#8211; it\u2019s your first impression, your positioning, and a key part of your sales funnel.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n                                <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-outline\" data-mp>\n              <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n              <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item>Let us take it out your hands<\/span>\n            <\/a>\n                    \n                  \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- awards-trails --><section class=\"section padded awards-trails inverted \">\n  <div class=\"bg bg-dark  bg-padded\">\n          <\/div>\n  <div class=\"relative container-wide\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"w-full\">\n        <div\n          class=\"text flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center z-500\" data-fade-in-childs>\n                      <div class=\"subtitle\">\n                <svg class=\"icon\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                    <use hre